a cross seller upsell standpoint. So some kind of really general business problems in the insurance

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:30.239
space. So that's kind of a high level overview of from a data science side. I think some of the

00:06:30.239 --> 00:06:36.399
things that are top of mind now. Cool. And when you say like when those opportunities, what does

00:06:36.399 --> 00:06:44.239
that actually mean for Beam Dental? Yeah. So for Beam, we sell insurance. And so we sell as any

