00:24:27.599 --> 00:24:32.400
myself and the analytics team for that portion of things, but it was also important to me that

00:24:32.400 --> 00:24:35.199
the candidate was kind of senior enough to have that exposure.

00:24:35.680 --> 00:24:41.280
And yeah, that's helpful, too. I'm just thinking more about, like, how you found candidates as

